                        "review": "What I love most is how clean and premium the experience feels — from the packaging to the results. It has honestly become a part of my daily self-care ritual."
                    }
                },
                { "type": "video", "settings": {} },
                {
                    "type": "text_block",
                    "settings": {
                        "author_name": "Sara Williams",
                        "rating": 4,
                        "review": "A genuinely thoughtful product. I appreciate the transparency in ingredients and the noticeable difference it makes to my day."
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
    ]
}
{% endschema %}
